libinstall v1.0

Author: Lázár Zoltán <lazi@compuserve.com>

Library extension installer for Amos Pro 2.x

This little command help you to install or remove intalled extensions,
and check which extensions are installed currently.
Everything is done without AmosPro.

Command templates:

check  - to get the extension name of a given slot
change - to change an extension slot
extnr=<x> - x holds the slot number
libname=<filename> - filename holds the extension file name

If you check a slot's contents, the result is pushed to the
$extname enviroment variable
